nd uptake of circulating amines, caution is advised.', 'Antagonism', NULL, NULL, 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/49135/', '[1] "Product Information. Mirvaso (brimonidine topical)." Galderma Laboratories Inc, Cranbury, NJ.[2] "Product Information. Alphagan (brimonidine ophthalmic)." Allergan Inc, Irvine, CA.', 1767363021);
